axine mepesuccinate, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Tagraxofusp, More', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/24746/', '[1] "Product Information. Xigris (drotrecogin alfa)." Lilly, Eli and Company, Indianapolis, IN.', 1767369485);
