erate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/24945/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] "Product Information. Diacomit (stiripentol)." Biocodex Inc, Creswell, OR.[3] EMEA. European Medicines Agency "EPARs. European Union Public Assessment Reports. Available from: URL: http://www.ema.europa.eu/ema/index.jsp?curl=pages/includes/medicines/medicines_landingpage.jsp&mid."[4] Canadian Pharmacists Association "e-CPS. Available from: URL: http://www.pharmacists.ca/function/Subscriptions/ecps.cfm?link=eCPS_quikLink."[5] EMEA. European Medicines Agency "EPARs. European Union Public Assessment Reports. Available from: URL: http://www.ema.europa.eu/ema/index.jsp?curl=pages/includes/medicines/medicines_landingpage.jsp&mid."[6] "Product Information. Diacomit (stiripentol)." Biocodex Inc, Creswell, OR.', 1767369485);
